@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.00)) + (0.68 * wp.exp(v1 + 0.07)))
    v1 = 0.15
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.10 * v1 + 0.49)))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.18)) * ((v1 + 0.48 * v2 + 0.58) * v2))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.77)))
    v2 = (0.26 + tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
